<para id="fs-idm274520224"><link class="lo-reference" document="m67921"/>Which financial statements do you need to calculate EPS?</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idm274687104">
<para id="fs-idm281852096">Comparative balance sheets and income statements.</para>
</solution>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idm276798224">
