<exercise id="fs-idm272473840">
<problem id="fs-idm272473584">
<para id="fs-idm274205792"><link class="lo-reference" document="m67921"/>Should investors rely on EPS as an investing tool? Why or why not?</para>
</problem>
<solution id="fs-idm270409120">
<para id="fs-idm273239184">Yes, as one analytical tool among others.</para>
</solution>
